data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully maintained, 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home in the heart of Hoschton. The timeless, updated kitchen showcases white shaker cabinets with contrasting black counters, white subway tile backsplash, stainless appliances, and a great view of the backyard. Don’t miss out on the private outdoor fenced backyard, perfect for entertaining or relaxing on the back porch or fire pit.  Conveniently located to I-85 and within walking distance of downtown Hoschton, this 1920 sqft home is perfect for a professional who works from home or a growing family.
